title: Fixes #1: Auto-adjusting chart ranges
message:
Fixes #1: Auto-adjusting chart ranges

- Chart ranges auto-adjust to fit at least 100 measurements.
- X-axis labels show values in time format (0, 1:23, 3:45:12,
  1d+1:23:45, etc).

Longer intervals support

title: Fixed SDK<11 compatibility
message:
Fixed SDK<11 compatibility

Checked on a 2.3 device, seems to work fine.

title: Added support for update interval units
message:
Added support for update interval units

The interval used to be 5...200 ms.
Now it can be the same range expressed in "ms", "sec", or "min".
The UI is a simple spinner.
